name: urea
Comments KP:
1. in original.xls they use an isocyanate reagent N=C=O but this will not work with regex as we also need to add a double bond. I used the carbamoyl chloride as equiv to isocyanate which will make sense to chemists. 10s of other methods to form ureas available.
2. Because of symmetry in urea N-C-N 2 C-N disconnections are possible, will be an issue to find which part is the scaffold and which the reagent
